{"id":5131,"date":"2018-06-06T18:22:52","date_gmt":"2018-06-06T12:52:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=5131"},"modified":"2022-02-17T15:06:08","modified_gmt":"2022-02-17T09:36:08","slug":"hidden-brains-awarded-iso-iec-27001-2013-certification-for-information-security-and-quality-management-systems","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hidden-brains-awarded-iso-iec-27001-2013-certification-for-information-security-and-quality-management-systems.html","title":{"rendered":"Gozoom Technologies Awarded ISO\/IEC 27001:2013 Certification for Information Security &#038; Quality Management Systems"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5132\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ISO-HB-Blog-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ISO-HB-Blog-1.png 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ISO-HB-Blog-1-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ISO-HB-Blog-1-768x373.png 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ISO-HB-Blog-1-600x291.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>It\u2019s a prestigious moment for Gozoom Technologies as it receives ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013 certificate. Meeting the extensive criteria for these standards, Gozoom Technologies emphasizes its commitment to information security of the clients\u2019 sensitive documents. This certificate also showcases our ability to consistently deliver the highest quality outputs by driving continuous improvements to products, services and internal processes.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Significance_of_ISOIEC_27001_2013\"><\/span>Significance of ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>ISO\/IEC 27001 is an information security standard that was last published in 2013 with the latest rules and regulations. It is published jointly by the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.iso.org\/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">International Organization for Standardization (ISO)<\/a> and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.iec.ch\/homepage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">International Electrotechnical Commission (IEC)<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>The ISO 27001:2013 Standard is a process-based approach established and updated regularly by the ISO, which is the world\u2019s largest developer of international standards. This standard mentions and clearly specifies the requirements for establishing, implementing, maintaining and continually improving an information security management system (ISMS) within the organization.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"A_Notable_Milestone_Hidden_Brains_Achieves_ISOIEC_27001_2013\"><\/span>A Notable Milestone: Gozoom Technologies Achieves ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Gozoom Technologies implemented all the necessary steps to comply with this standard. Accredited and authorized auditors performed assessment of the organization&#8217;s ISMS to confirm its complete compliance with the ISO 27001:2013 requirements and thereafter ISO\/IEC 27001:2013 certificate was issued. By achieving this certification, we can now identify, control and eliminate security risks through certified security practices.<\/p>\n<p>This certificate is a testament to Gozoom Technologies\u2019 commitment to accessibility, confidentiality and integrity of information. This recognition from ISO is the result of streamlined technology processes, operations and internal data practices. The breadth of Gozoom Technologies certification ensures continuity of data stewardship through the entire service delivery process.<\/p>\n<p>This is an effective demonstration of company\u2019s commitment to ongoing improvement and dedication to maintain high standard of Information Security Management System (ISMS). We will work tirelessly to achieve the quality standards that our customers\u2019 demand.<\/p>\n<p>This is a moment of pride for Gozoom Technologies as ISO\/IEC 27001:2013 is only awarded to companies that comply with the defined standards and pass the test of accredited, independent auditors.<\/p>\n<p>The ISO 27001:2013 award certifies Gozoom Technologies has the capability to thoroughly evaluate or identify risks and appropriate measures in place to handle or minimize them. This certificate reassures that the company operates with a comprehensive set of information security controls and risk management measures to address security risks within its hosted services and corporate environment. We respect the security and safety of client\u2019s information and ensure that the information security controls meet the information security needs of both stakeholders and customers on an ongoing basis.<\/p>\n<p>We are proud to have earned this certification that attests our highest level of controls in handling client\u2019s confidential information.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hidden-brains-awarded-iso-iec-27001-2013-certification-for-information-security-and-quality-management-systems.html\/#Significance_of_ISOIEC_27001_2013\" title=\"Significance of ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013\">Significance of ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hidden-brains-awarded-iso-iec-27001-2013-certification-for-information-security-and-quality-management-systems.html\/#A_Notable_Milestone_Hidden_Brains_Achieves_ISOIEC_27001_2013\" title=\"A Notable Milestone: Gozoom Technologies Achieves ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013\">A Notable Milestone: Gozoom Technologies Achieves ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It\u2019s a prestigious moment for Gozoom Technologies as it receives ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013 certificate. Meeting the extensive criteria for these standards, Gozoom Technologies emphasizes its commitment to information security of the clients\u2019 sensitive documents. This certificate also showcases our ability to consistently deliver the highest quality outputs by driving continuous improvements to products, services and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5132,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":{"show_blog_end":"no","add_blog_end":"","display_hellobar":false,"add_hellobar":"","add_hellobar_link":"","bottom_cta_text":"","bottom_cta_link":"","featured_posts":["no"],"add_text":"","text_color":"#000000","top_cta_text":"","top_cta_link":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Gozoom Technologies Awarded ISO\/IEC 27001:2013 Certification for Information Security &amp; Quality Management Systems - Gozoom Technologies Blog<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Gozoom Technologies receives the most valuable ISO\/IEC 27001: 2013 certification. This certificate is intended to bring information security and quality under management control.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/w